tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE digital_art_metadata (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  dimensions VARCHAR(50),
  resolution VARCHAR(20),
  creation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE artwork_metadata (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    dimensions VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    resolution VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    creation_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE artist_info (
    artist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    artist_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    nationality VARCHAR(50),
    style VARCHAR(50),
    birth_year INT
);

CREATE TABLE digital_art_metadata (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name TEXT,
    dimensions TEXT,
    resolution TEXT,
    creation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE digital_art_files (id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 dimensions VARCHAR(50),

CREATE TABLE artists (artist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 artist_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
 nationality VARCHAR(50),
 birth_date DATE,

CREATE TABLE galleries (gallery_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 gallery_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
 location VARCHAR(255),
 num_artworks INT)

CREATE TABLE art_collections (collection_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 collection_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
 curator VARCHAR(100),
 num_artworks INT,
 creation_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE digital_art_files (
    id INT NOT NULL,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    dimensions VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, 
    resolution VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, 
    creation_date DATE NOT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
